<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Cyobb</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= Rails.configuration.lkp['description'] %>">
  <meta name="keywords" content="<%= Rails.configuration.lkp['keywords'] %>">

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/simplemde/latest/simplemde.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/marked/0.3.6/marked.min.js"></script>
    <!-- google recaptcha -->
    <script src='https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js'></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
      <div class="container-fluid container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><%= Rails.configuration.lkp['title'] %></a>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav">

          </ul>

          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <% if current_user %>
              <li><%= link_to('Text editor guide', 'https://simplemde.com/markdown-guide',{target: '_blank'}) %></li>
              <li><%= link_to('Update blog details', update_blog_path) %></li>
              <li><%= link_to('Logout', destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete) %></li>
            <% else %>
              <li><%= link_to "Sign up", new_registration_path(resource_name) %></li>
              <li><%= link_to "Log in", new_session_path(resource_name) %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
      <main>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-9 little-padding">
            <% if notice %>
              <p class="alert alert-success"><%= notice %></p>
            <% end %>
            <% if alert %>
              <p class="alert alert-danger"><%= alert %></p>
            <% end %>
            <%= yield %>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <h2>Look Ups</h2>
            <% if current_user %>
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-body">
                  Your blog is published at<br>
                  <a href="<%= Rails.configuration.lkp['base_url'] %>/<%= current_user.username %>" target="_blank">
                    <%= Rails.configuration.lkp['base_url'] %>/<%= current_user.username %>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">Publish the changes</div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                  <a href="/blogs/publish" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Publish Changes</a><br>
                  Changes may take upto 5 minutes to reflect.
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-body">
                  You have written
                  <!-- <!%= current_user.blogs.first.posts.count %> posts. -->
                </div>
                <div class="panel-footer">
                  <!-- Last published at <!%= current_user.blogs.first.last_published_at %> -->
                  <!-- <!%= current_user.blogs.first.last_published_status %> -->
                </div>
              </div>
            <% else %>
              <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-body">
                  Your blog will be published at<br>
                  <%= Rails.configuration.lkp['base_url'] %>/username
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Explain the concept</h1>
        <p>After you sign up we create and publish your blog online
           and after that you can add and edit blogs right here and publish them with one button.
           We take care of all the deployment, design and seo and what not. You have to just write content
            at which you are awesome right.
            If you don't like your url address we have created for you, you can always buy your own url from godaddy.com for around
            Rs. 500 / 7.734 USD and use that url to publish your blog.
         </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/pages/learn_more">Learn more</a></p>
      </div>
      <footer>Copyright &copy; 2013-2017 <a href="https://github.com/rajatsingla">Rajatsingla.in</a> (rajatrs5054 at gmail.com)</footer>
    </div>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/simplemde/latest/simplemde.min.css">
  </body>
</html>
